edu.ncsu.csc216.howlondemand.model

Class AudioTrack

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.howlondemand.model.Multimedia
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.howlondemand.model.AudioTrack

  • public class AudioTrack
extends Multimedia
    Concrete child class of Multimedia. Represents an audio track that can be streamed. Has a numerical id, title, artist and a collection of track chunk data to be used when streaming.
    Author:
    Noah Benveniste
